QuestData.Title: Fishing: Aileron Seamoth
QuestData.Description:
Doesn't ANYBODY know how to fish PROPERLY anymore?
<Lukoturukk wiggles his nose angrily.>
You, with the face, go get me some fish. GOOD fish. And no grungles!
QuestData.LogDescription: Fish up $1oa Aileron Seamoths from the ocean around the Dragon Isles.
